
#Setting login
POST /setlogin
parameters: username password
create cookie with username, dont worry about password

#get tickets that I can view as worker
GET /tickets/worker
filter through the group_member table to get all groups my user id is a part of and then filter the group_categories for those ids and then filter tickets by those categories

#get tickets that I have submitted
GET /tickets/customer
filter the ticket table by submitted_by the user who requests

#submit a new ticket
POST /tickets/new
parameters: user group category title description
add new ticket with newly generated guid status of new, and auto fill the timestamp




